---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home" description="PyCon 2025 - Annual Python conference bringing together developers from around the world.">
  <style>
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3776ab 0%, #2d5f8d 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background-image: url('/pycon-2025/assets/event-image-1.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      opacity: 0.15;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #ffd43b;
      color: #2c3e50;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #ffed4e;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .section {
      margin: 4rem 0;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #3776ab;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #ffd43b;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .schedule-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .schedule-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 4px solid #3776ab;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .schedule-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .schedule-card h3 {
      color: #3776ab;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .schedule-card p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }

    .venue-info {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .venue-card {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .venue-card h3 {
      color: #3776ab;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .venue-card p {
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .register-form {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #333;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #3776ab;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(55, 118, 171, 0.1);
    }

    .submit-button {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #3776ab;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .submit-button:hover {
      background-color: #2d5f8d;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      .hero p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .section h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .venue-info {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>PyCon 2025</h1>
      <p>Annual Python conference bringing together developers from around the world.</p>
      <a href="#register" class="cta-button">Register Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="section">
    <h2>About PyCon 2025</h2>
    <p>
      PyCon 2025 is the premier annual conference for the Python community. Join thousands of developers, data scientists, and Python enthusiasts from around the globe for three days of inspiring talks, hands-on workshops, and networking opportunities.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether you're a beginner just starting your Python journey or an experienced developer, PyCon 2025 offers something for everyone. Learn from industry experts, discover cutting-edge tools and frameworks, and connect with fellow Python enthusiasts.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="schedule" class="section">
    <h2>Schedule Highlights</h2>
    <div class="schedule-grid">
      <div class="schedule-card">
        <h3>Day 1: Keynotes & Workshops</h3>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> May 15, 2025</p>
        <p>Opening keynotes from industry leaders and hands-on workshops covering Python fundamentals and advanced topics.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-card">
        <h3>Day 2: Technical Talks</h3>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> May 16, 2025</p>
        <p>Deep-dive technical presentations on web development, data science, machine learning, and more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-card">
        <h3>Day 3: Sprints & Networking</h3>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> May 17, 2025</p>
        <p>Open-source sprints, lightning talks, and evening networking reception.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="venue" class="section">
    <h2>Venue Information</h2>
    <div class="venue-info">
      <div class="venue-card">
        <h3>📍 Location</h3>
        <p><strong>Convention Center</strong></p>
        <p>123 Tech Boulevard</p>
        <p>San Francisco, CA 94105</p>
        <p>United States</p>
      </div>
      <div class="venue-card">
        <h3>🚀 Getting There</h3>
        <p><strong>Public Transportation:</strong> BART and Muni accessible</p>
        <p><strong>Parking:</strong> On-site parking available</p>
        <p><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Fully wheelchair accessible</p>
        <p><strong>Accommodations:</strong> Hotel partnerships available</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="register" class="section">
    <h2>Register for PyCon 2025</h2>
    <form class="register-form" method="POST" action="#">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="name">Full Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required aria-label="Full Name" />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="email">Email Address</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required aria-label="Email Address" />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="company">Company/Organization</label>
        <input type="text" id="company" name="company" aria-label="Company or Organization" />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="message">Additional Information</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" aria-label="Additional Information"></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="submit-button">Register</button>
    </form>
  </section>
</Layout>